@endnode
@node CLOUD "Cloud Spirit"

@{b}Cloud Spirit@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(C)
Type    = Summon Spirit (3/1)
Cost    = 2U
Artist  = Randy Gallegos

Text(SH): Flying
          Cloud Spirit can block only creatures with flying.

Flavor Text: @{i}Clouds are the soil, dreams are the crop. -Kor saying@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node CONTE "Contempt"

@{b}Contempt@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(C)
Type    = Enchant Creature
Cost    = 1U
Artist  = Val Mayerik

Text(SH): If enchanted creature attacks, return that creature and Contempt
          to owner's hand at end of combat.

Flavor Text: @{i}"Predictable little man. In all these years you taught
             me so much yet learned so little." -Volrath, to Starke
@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node DREAH "Dream Halls"

@{b}Dream Halls@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(R)
Type    = Enchantment
Cost    = 3UU
Artist  = Matthew Wilson

Text(SH): Instead of paying the casting cost for a spell of any color, its
          caster may choose and discard a card that shares at least one
          color with that spell. If the spell has X in its casting cost, X
          is 0.

Flavor Text: @{i}Within without.@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node DREAP "Dream Prowler"

@{b}Dream Prowler@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(C)
Type    = Summon Illusion (1/5)
Cost    = 2UU
Artist  = Richard Kane Ferguson

Text(SH): Dream Prowler is unblockable as long as no other creatures are
          attacking.

Flavor Text: @{i}"To think that some find sleep a restful state." -Volrath@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node EVACU "Evacuation"

@{b}Evacuation@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(R)
Type    = Instant
Cost    = 3UU
Artist  = Rob Alexander

Text(SH): Return all creatures to owner's hands.

Flavor Text: @{i}The first step of every exodus is from the blood and
             the fire onto the trail@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node GLIDI "Gliding Licid"

@{b}Gliding Licid@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(U)
Type    = Summon Licid (2/2)
Cost    = 2U
Artist  = Heather Hudson

Text(SH): <UT>: Gliding Licid loses this ability and becomes a creature
          enchantment that reads "Enchanted creature gains flying" instead
          of a creature. Move Gliding Licid onto target creature.  You may
          pay U to end this effect.


 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node HAMME "Hammerhead Shark"

@{b}Hammerhead Shark@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(C)
Type    = Summon Fish (2/3)
Cost    = 1U
Artist  = Stephen Daniele

Text(SH): Hammerhead Shark cannot attack unless defending player controls
          any islands.

Flavor Text: @{i}Cross the eyes of a hammerhead and you'll dot its teeth.@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node HESIT "Hesitation"

@{b}Hesitation@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(U)
Type    = Enchantment
Cost    = 1U
Artist  = Pete Venters

Text(SH): If any spell is played, counter that spell and sacrifice
          Hesitation.

Flavor Text: @{i}Gerrard hesitaed, looking up at an enemy ship. The future
             hesitated with him, changed forever by the pause.
@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node INTRU "Intruder Alarm"

@{b}Intruder Alarm@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(R)
Type    = Enchantment
Cost    = 2U
Artist  = Donato Giancola

Text(SH): Creatures do not untap during their controllers' untap phase.
          Whenever any creature comes into play, untap all creatures.

Flavor Text: @{i}Mirri was startled by Volrath's apparition- it had no scent.@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node LEAP_ "Leap"

@{b}Leap@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(C)
Type    = Instant
Cost    = U
Artist  = Kev Walker

Text(SH): Target creature gains flying until end of turn. Draw a card.

Flavor Text: @{i}Mirri leapt quickly and silently. The Guard died likewise.@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node MANAL "Mana Leak"

@{b}Mana Leak@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(C)
Type    = Interrupt
Cost    = 1U
Artist  = Christopher Rush

Text(SH): Counter target spell unless its caster pays an additional 3.

Flavor Text: @{i}"The fatal flaw in every plan is the assumption that
             you know more than your enemy." -Volrath
@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node MASKO "Mask of the Mimic"

@{b}Mask of the Mimic@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(U)
Type    = Instant
Cost    = U
Artist  = Heather Hudson

Text(SH): Sacrifice a creature: Search your library for any copy of target
          creature card and put it into play. Shuffle your library
          afterwards.


 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node MINDG "Mind Games"

@{b}Mind Games@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(C)
Type    = Instant
Cost    = U
Artist  = Andrew Robinson

Text(SH): Buyback 2U (You may pay an additional 2U when you play this
          spell. If you do, put it into your hand insted of your graveyard
          as part of the spell's effect.)
          Tap target artifact, creature, or land.


 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node RANSA "Ransack"

@{b}Ransack@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(U)
Type    = Sorcery
Cost    = 3U
Artist  = Ron Spencer

Text(SH): Look at the top five cards of target player's library. Put any
          number of those cards on the bottom of that player's library in
          any order and the rest on top of the player's library in any
          order.


 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node REBOU "Rebound"

@{b}Rebound@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(U)
Type    = Interrupt
Cost    = 1U
Artist  = Doug Chaffee

Text(SH): Target spell, which targets only a single player, targets another
          player of your choice instead.

Flavor Text: @{i}Insult, like an arrow, is beyond control once loosed.@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node REINS "Reins of Power"

@{b}Reins of Power@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(R)
Type    = Instant
Cost    = 2UU
Artist  = Colin Mc Neil

Text(SH): You and target oppenent each untap and  gain control of all
          creatures the other controls until end of turn. Those creatures
          are unaffected by summoning sickness this turn.


 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node SIFT_ "Sift"

@{b}Sift@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(C)
Type    = Sorcery
Cost    = 3U
Artist  = Pete Venters

Text(SH): Draw three cards, then choose and discard a card.

Flavor Text: @{i}Twice I have let the Legacy slip away. Never again."
             -Karn, silver golem
@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node SILVE "Silver Wyvern"

@{b}Silver Wyvern@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(R)
Type    = Summon Drake (4/3)
Cost    = 3UU
Artist  = Colin Mc Neil

Text(SH): Flying
          <U>: Target spell or ability, which targets only Silver Wyvern,
          targets another creature of your choice instead. Play this
          ability as an interrupt.


 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node SPIND "Spindrift Drake"

@{b}Spindrift Drake@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(C)
Type    = Summon Drake (2/1)
Cost    = U
Artist  = Anthony Waters

Text(SH): Flying
          During your upkeep, pay U or sacrifce Spindrift Drake.

Flavor Text: @{i}Sea brine for blood, washing foam for laughter.@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node THALA "Thalakos Deceiver"

@{b}Thalakos Deceiver@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(R)
Type    = Summon Wizard (1/1)
Cost    = 3U
Artist  = Andrew Robinson

Text(SH): Shadow (This creature can block or be blocked by only creatures
          with shadow.)
          Sacrifice Thalakos Deceiver: Gain control of target creature
          permanently. Use this ability only if Thalakos Deceiver is
          attacking and unblocked.


 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node TIDAS "Tidal Surge"

@{b}Tidal Surge@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(C)
Type    = Sorcery
Cost    = 1U
Artist  = Doug Chaffee

Text(SH): Tap up to three target creatures without flying.

Flavor Text: @{i}"It is nature that gives us our boundaries and
             nature that enforces them."
@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node TIDAW "Tidal Warrior"

@{b}Tidal Warrior@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(C)
Type    = Summon Merfolk (1/1)
Cost    = U
Artist  = Daren Bader

Text(SH): <T>: Target land is an island until end of turn.

Flavor Text: @{i}The tide of battle favors those who can swim.@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node VOLRA "Volrath's Shapeshifter"

@{b}Volrath's Shapeshifter@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(R)
Type    = Summon Shapeshifter (0/1)
Cost    = 1UU
Artist  = Ron Spencer

Text(SH): As long as the top card of your graveyard is a creature card,
          Volrath's Shapeshifter is a copy of that card, except that
          Volrath's Shapeshifter retains its abilities.
          <2>: Choose and discard a card.


 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node WALKI "Walking Dream"

@{b}Walking Dream@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(U)
Type    = Summon Illusion (3/3)
Cost    = 3U
Artist  = Richard Kane Ferguson

Text(SH): Walking Dream is unblockable.
          Walking Dream does not untap during your untap phase if any
          opponent controls two or more creatures.

Flavor Text: @{i}Dreams, by definition, live shorter lives than
             those who dream them.
@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node WALLT "Wall of Tears"

@{b}Wall of Tears@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = SH(U)
Type    = Summon Wall (0/4)
Cost    = 1U
Artist  = Rebecca Guay

Text(SH): (Walls cannot attack.)
          If Wall of Tears blocks any creatures, return each of those
          creatures to owner's hand at end of combat.

Flavor Text: @{i}"Many have been lost to pity." -Karn, silver golem@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
